Package org.hibernate.bytecode.internal.none

Class BytecodeProviderImpl

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.bytecode.internal.none.BytecodeProviderImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, BytecodeProvider, Service
public final class BytecodeProviderImpl extends Object implements BytecodeProvider
This BytecodeProvider represents the "no-op" enhancer; mostly useful as an optimisation when not needing any byte code optimisation applied, for example when the entities have been enhanced at compile time. Choosing this BytecodeProvider allows to exclude the bytecode enhancement libraries from the runtime classpath.
Since:
5.4
